snippet.title: The Foglands Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW!
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/636190/The_Foglands/
PlayStation - https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10003574/

The Foglands is an atmospheric roguelike adventure where you’ll discover new paths and uncover old secrets. Run into the unknown, fight monsters, scavenge loot, and try to make it back before you are swallowed by the fog.

Coming in 2023 to Playstation VR2 and Quest 2.
TBA - Steam

Game - https://www.thefoglands.com
Studio - https://www.welltold.games
Twitter - https://twitter.com/WellToldEnt
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/bnm9FyHddC

Game Composer - Jason Gallaty: https://theophany-rmx.bandcamp.com/music
Track: The Foglands Announcement Trailer
Artists: Jason Gallaty, Mahawam, Natalyn Daniels, Alejandro Pérez Heinze

#thefoglands #welltold #psvr2 #quest2
